Parameters:

windDirection - The current wind direction (in degrees).
description - A human-readable description of the current weather.
imageUrl - A url pointing to a picture that describes the weather.
visibility - How far you can see (in miles).
windchill - The perceived temperature (in Fahrenheit).
pressure - The barometric pressure (in inches).
